title: Microsoft.MS.Visual.Studio.MASM.32.64.ARM.MIPS.CPP.1990.to.2015
description:
Microsoft.MS.Visual.Studio.MASM.32.64.ARM.MIPS.CPP.1990.to.2015

Microsoft Visual Studio Assorted Collection 1998 to 2015.
(MASM and C/C++ target platform: intel-32. AMD-64 and ARM).

Special guests:
  - Borland's 32-bit Turbo Debugger 5.5
  - The legendary MASM 6.11 CodeView (original, uninstalled)
  - MASM 5! dated as old as '87 in my ATX 16-MHz 80286 IBM PC
    (16-bit only though, not very useful)

Assembler/Compiler ONLY!
